<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Denying Jesus as the Christ is the worst offense there is in this regard.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">This doesn't mean just outright denial and blasphemy either. Denial can take the form of attributing false characteristics to the character of Jesus.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Denial can mean praising God while making up excuses for not needing Jesus or trying to replace Jesus with someone or something else.</li></ul></body></html>